  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">A</span> Interact</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Your mind becomes clear and cognition flows freely, but physical matters seem ephemeral.</p>\n<p><strong>Benefit</strong> You gain a +3 item bonus to Arcana, Crafting, Lore, Occultism, and Society checks and all checks to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.1OagaWtBpVXExToo]{Recall Knowledge}. Your critical failures on Recall Knowledge checks become failures instead. You become trained in one Intelligence-based skill [Arcana, Crafting, Lore, Occultism, Society], chosen at creation.</p>\n<p><strong>Drawback</strong> You take a -2 penalty to weapon and unarmed attack rolls, Athletics checks, and acrobatics checks. You can carry 2 less Bulk than normal before becoming encumbered, and the maximum Bulk you can carry is reduced by 4.</p>\n<p><strong>Duration</strong> 1 hour.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-effects.Item.qit1mLbJUyRTYcPU]{Effect: Cognitive Mutagen (Greater)}</p>"
